  "description": "<i>ACME Animation Factory</i> is essentially <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/mario-paint\">Mario Paint</a> with a <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?gamegroup=Looney+Tunes+licensees\">Looney Tunes license</a>.  The player can choose from 18 pre-set animations of their favorite cartoon characters and super impose them over a scene to create their very own cartoon.  Much like <i>Mario Paint</i>, they can also color blank drawings, create their own music and even play games like <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Solitaire\">Solitaire</a> and Mix 'n' Match.  Players can also save their own creations for later viewing.",
